In BigBot Crew, a bunch of techy teens are building the robots of the future!

Based on the proven game design in our hit game Northern Sky, Blue Treasure will take you on an exciting underwater safari with a bunch of pirates!

Get your scuba gear on and descend into the depths of the ocean  it's a truly fascinating world down there. Explore the sunken ship under the watchful eye of a giant octopus and other curious creatures. Will you find the hidden treasure at the bottom of the sea?

title: Crown of Valor
description:
Burning rocks hurled at castle walls and knights armed with heavy battle axes and siege weapons  welcome to the Dark Ages.

We're throwing you smack-bang into the middle of an intense castle siege. Will you be able to get through the gates to get your hands on the treasures on the other side?

Crown of Valor is an extremely volatile 5x5 cluster game with clusters of five or more symbols, plus a max exposure of around 15,000x bet!
The features include tumble mechanics, progressive Multipliers, a Free Spins Bonus, and a Bonus Buy feature! 

With gorgeous state-of-the-art graphics made with the same 3D engine as Nero's Fortune, this blockbuster release packs a punch.

title: Crystal Prince
description:
Forget Santa's Lapland this winter and come visit the Crystal Prince instead! The star of this show is a charming and generous guy who takes good care of his visitors  you can win up to 11,500 x your bet!

When the Crystal Prince swings his magic wand around, he can create Golden Wilds and Multipliers. And sometimes he even flies into the Northern Lights and spreads his wealth over the people of his land, so make sure to be around when that happens.

title: Crystal Queen
description:
Crystal Queen is based on the HC Andersen story about the Snow Queen, and is an innovative slot which is loads of fun.

The game features swooping reels, spreading wild symbols, win multipliers, and up to 6 rows!

In the Free Spins bonus all 6 rows are unlocked, and the game pays both ways! With the addition of a fantastic soundtrack, and an extremely well balance math, Crystal Queen is truly one of our flagship games.

title: Diamond Duke
description: Classic diamonds, sevens and cherries  Diamond Duke is a real nostalgia trip!With a look and feel inspired by 1950s jukeboxes, this game will transport you to the heyday of American diners and classic cars with chrome and wings. Why not cruise to the diner for some pancakes and milkshake?Instead of the usual reels filling the screen, this game has an actual slot machine inside the game! And the symbols, the animations, and the music really make it feel like you're playing an old-school slot.This 5-line, 3-reel slot boasts high volatility, a super valuable diamond symbol, two bonus wheels, and a Pick & Click bonus for players who like great highs and lows and you can win up to 8,000 x your bet!

title: Dinosaur Rage
description:
Anna the Explorer is back from The Ark of Mystery and this time she's battling a bunch of enraged dinosaurs.

Dinosaur Rage is a 4?5 slot with 1,024 ways, high volatility, and the chance to win up to 17,000 x your bet! This game expands our range of high maximum exposure games and combines proven game mechanics with completely new ones.

The features include a Pay Anywhere feature, a Dinosaur Rage! Free Spins bonus (up to 25 spins), a Free Spins Re-trigger, growing symbols, and a Bonus Buy feature with two modes pay 75x or 150x your bet and get instant entry to the Dinosaur Rage! Free Spins bonus!

In the Free Spins bonus, at least one of the dinosaurs will grow to 4 symbols high and always include the Pay Anywhere feature (all dinosaurs can get this feature at the same time!).

title: Divine Dreams
description:
In Divine Dreams, the Goddess of Wealth and Prosperity welcomes you deep inside a dreamy rainforest, where you'll find calming visuals and serene music. It's like a little moment of mindfulness in your busy day!

The game is set within the rainforests of an Indonesian island, where the Goddess of Wealth and Prosperity lives. The people of the island create beautiful artefacts that worship her and the nature around her, and she's believed to bring successful harvest to them.

These valuable artefacts, the connection with nature, and the spirituality of this setting, is what we've designed the symbols around in this slot. It's a very peaceful game, but it's still highly volatile and packed with tons of cool features  like the Mystical Multiplier that multiplies each win!

Step into this dreamy rainforest today to find out what the Goddess has in store for you.

title: Dragon Chase
description: This long-anticipated 3x5 reel slot with 20 bet lines boasts a stunning Asian theme with lots of red, gold and traditional symbols all to the tunes of beautiful music!With a fiery dragon that breathes Wildfires onto the reels, a Free Spins Bonus, and a Dragon Pearl Respin feature with 4 jackpot levels, this slot is guaranteed to give you a fun, unique and thrilling gaming experience! And the larger your bet, the greater your chances of winning the GRAND jackpot!Dragon Chase is so much more than your standard slot game, as it's both a great slot game and a jackpot game. And that's not all. We've also made TWO versions of the game, which is completely unique  so you get two for the price of one!Operators can choose to run one version or both, which lets you target a wider range of players at the same time. The game will have multijurisdictional support and it will use an operator specific/local jackpot.This slot will appeal to all types of players, as seasoned players will love the traditional theme and casual players will love the clear message and fun features!

title: Dragon Shrine
description:
Welcome to Dragon Shrine, a colourful and exciting 40 betlines game, featuring the Dragon Stack Respin feature.

The excitement is turned up in Free Spins with a double stack feature, filling both the left and right reels with Dragons.

The artwork gives a modern twist to a classic theme.

title: Durian Dynamite
description: Durian Dynamite is a classic fruit game in a modern package, combining stunning 3D graphics with unique features and highly volatile gameplay!

title: Dwarfs Gone Wild
description:
In Dwarfs Gone Wild, join Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs as they dig for hidden underground treasures!

The game is set deep inside a mine shaft, and each of the seven dwarfs possess unique powers that help create an explosive gameplay filled with bonus features and free spins!

The Golden minecarts unlock special Dwarf features when the free spins bonus is triggered, and every win that includes a Dwarf symbol is added to the Golden Minecart Bonus meter. The famous beauty's mirror is also a key feature in this slot, and when triggered, it will reward 300 additional symbols and two free spins!

Paying homage to the classic fairy tale, Dwarfs Gone Wild features Hollywood style animations and a folksy soundtrack that adds authenticity to this exciting game!

title: Eastern Emeralds
description: Eastern Emeralds is set in the heart of the Asian wilderness, against a beautiful backdrop of steep mountains. This extremely volatile game is jam-packed with golden opportunities!

title: Fairy Gate
description:
Deep down in the woods there is a fairy tale adventure waiting to happen thanks to our latest release, the Fairy Gate.

This enchanted encounter begins its flight of fancy when the magical tree opens up to reveal fairy orbs lighting up the screen to award wild symbols

The 3?5 slot features all kinds of fairies, with three bonus symbols triggering the free spins feature.

title: Genies Touch
description:
The touch of the Genie is something to behold as she uses her powers to change symbols.

 

Three or more magic lamp symbols triggers the Genie's Touch feature as she appears out of each lamp and turns adjacent symbols into matching symbols, always picking the best win combination!
If that's not enough, there is a Free Spins game with extra magic lamp symbols to keep the fun coming.

title: Ghost Glyph
description:
Just in time for Halloween, we welcome you to an old haunted house. Hidden underneath the grounds ghosts have a life of their own, each with its own unique ability, quirkiness and characteristics.

Ghost Glyph is a well-balanced cluster game with medium volatility, a 31% hit rate in the base game and up to 2,200x in exposure. The charming poltergeists are just the cherry on the top! Expect a spooky gaming experience with a splash of colour.

title: Golden Glyph
description: Channel your inner Indiana Jones and get ready to embark on an epic adventure in the land of the Pharaohs. Spin the reels, wait for the dust to settle, and let the hieroglyphs reveal your fortune.This stunning and feature-rich slot boasts a 7x7 layout that's perfect for our new portrait mode! The features include Tumble Mechanics, a Power Wild feature, and a Power-Up feature with four magical Power-Ups: Golden Scarab, Eye of Horus, Blaze of Fire, and a Free Spins Bonus.

title: Golden Glyph 2
description:
Every great game deserves a sequel, wouldn't you agree? Get ready to return to the land of the Pharaohs, we're taking you on another unforgettable trip to Egypt with Golden Glyph 2.

The original title was our first ever cluster game and now we've revamped everything and given it an extra boost  enjoy improved game design, higher hit rates, and even smoother gameplay!
In addition to our new Bonus Buy feature (pay to get instant entry to the Free Spins bonus), this game boasts great Respins and a even more exciting power-ups!

description:
Who’s been eating my porridge? It’s Goldilocks of course – the world’s most famous breakfast thief is back!

But don’t be fooled by her sweet and innocent exterior, this troublesome golden girl is naughtier than ever before in this fabulous and feature-rich slot.

If she’s feeling nice though, she might lead you into the Free Spins Bonus game where you can win big! And while you’re there, let her tease the bears to tu

title: Gold Lab
description:
Gold Lab is a bright and fun game, featuring our little scientist and his quest to make gold.

The main feature of the game is trigger symbols, which turn ordinary low paying symbols into wilds, for 4 or more respins.

title: Guardian of Athens
description:
Pack your toga and travel to ancient Greece with Guardian of Athens – you’ll fit right in. Immerse yourself in history and marvel at the magnificent architecture and grand statues. And there’s something else to marvel at: the reels are full of gold. Lots of gold.

This 3×5 slot with 20 bet lines boasts high volatility and a max exposure of 16,000x bet, together with proven and popular game mechanics like Multiplier Wilds and an exciting Free Spins Bonus!

Enter the building to the bonus game and float above the clouds, where you’ll be asked to choose your fate. Feeling brave? There are four options to choose from – the higher the risk, the higher the reward.

This game design is a proven concept based on player data from one of our biggest hit games: Eastern Emeralds. The Free Spins mode in particular has been extremely appreciated by players, as they really like the option to choose their own

title: Hidden Valley 120

Hidden Valley is based on the fictional story of Shangri-La, a mystical valley and an earthly paradise  an eternal happy land, hidden from the world!

In this game, two travelers in Tibet have found the secret entrance to this valley, and they're heading towards it with their Sherpa. Join these adventurers on their quest, and discover a gorgeous Tibetan landscape filled with exciting features all to the tunes of beautiful music.

The main feature in this beautiful game is the Stacked Wilds, and there's also a Random Wild multiplier that can multiply up to x10! The Free Spins give you a chance to win extra spins, or to turn regular symbols into Wilds for an opportunity to win BIG!

Illuminous means bright, and bright is what this game is

The animations, and feedback of the game are astonishing. It has a respin feature that initiates two or more reels with about 50% wilds on the reel strips.

In free spins you have at least three of the reels with extra wilds.

title: Ivan and the Immortal King
description:
Ivan and the Immortal King is based on an old classic Russian fairy tale, so this game will take you on a one-of-a-kind adventure!

Your mission is the slay the immortal Kind Koschey, but there's just one problem: his soul is hidden inside a needle, which is in an egg, which is in a duck, which is in a hare, which is in a chest. So, all you have to do is find the chest, kill the hare, capture the duck, open the egg, and break the needle! Easy, right?

Get your sword, strap your boots on, and go find out if you have what it takes to defeat the king and cease all his gold!

With an extremely volatile gameplay and tons of exciting features, like Super High Paying Symbols, the Baba Yaga Mystery Surprise, and Free Spins with increasing Multipliers, this game is a fairy tale come true!

title: Joker Strike
description:
Joker Strike is a game that's bound to put a smile on your face!

But don't be fooled by its fun appearance, this game is built on the very same mechanics that made our Second Strike such a smash hit, so it's no joke.

This highly volatile slot boasts a Joker Strike feature, which is triggered by any win, and an awesome Hi Roller feature that offers you a chance of even higher wins and more thrills  bet big to win BIG!

Make sure you're there when this joker strikes!

This wealth themed slot is a very straight forward game with stacked King Colossus symbols, and stacked Wild symbols

With guaranteed wilds on reel 1, and possibly reel 5 for each spin you will get mega large wins combined withthe massive King Colossus symbol. Chase the bonus and see for yourself!

title: Leprechaun Hills
description: Make mischief with the leprechauns in this 4?5 reel, 40-line video slot featuring lucky respins and rainbow free spins. The game celebrates all things Irish, with symbols including a pint of the country's famous stout, leprechauns and magic fungi.

title: Loco the Monkey
description:
Ever wondered what it would be like to be a monkey for a day? Here’s your chance!

This junglelicious adventure will take you to a special place where Loco (the monkey) lives. It’s a green haven full of exotic plants and clean air, plus an abundance of yummy pineapples, bananas, mangos, and blueberries. A feast for the eyes as well as the belly.

And Loco isn’t the only ape in town, there’s also a special golden monkey to befriend… get three on the reels to trigger the Free Spins bonus.

This fun-filled 4×5 slot with 50 lines include a Monkey Frenzy! Free Spins bonus and a More Monkeys! Respin feature – and the chance to win ove

The legends tell of Mayan gold and there are riches galore to be had in this super sticky game, with its innovative new functionality.

What starts as a 3x3 game which respins on any win, expands into a 3?5 one as the respins keep on coming. Any 3 or more connected symbols will stick, whether in the middle, on the left, or to the right.
There are also multipliers for the respin wins, and a randomly-triggered Mucha Mayana feature, which can add up to a 20 x multiplier to the last golden win!

title: Midas Coins
description:
Who said all that glitters is not gold? They must not have played Midas Coins.

Welcome to ancient Greece and the land of King Midas. As legend has it, everything this king touches turns to gold. Slightly annoying for him perhaps, but great for you.

There's an abundance of bling on these reels: rings, necklaces, earrings, and more. All in that sweet glittering gold.

In this 5x3 slot with 25 lines, the game mechanics include a Coin Collect feature (collect coins to grow your stack), an All is Golden Free Spins bonus where you can grow your stack even more, plus a Bonus Buy feature (pay to get instant entry to the Free Spins bonus)!

title: Mighty Arthur
description:
King Arthur and his sorcerer Merlin are the stuff of fantasy, but this pair are very real  being full reel wild symbols with different powers.

Watch Merlin summon his magic to scatter the reels with wild symbols. Hit his royal master and he will expand to cover three reels and create a massive wild symbol with guaranteed massive wins.

title: Hall of the Mountain King
description: This game was inspired by the famous classical music piece! In the Hall of the Mountain King by Edvard Grieg, which plays a central part in the slot.Any win can be multiplied by landing wilds (up to 15x in the Free Spins Bonus!), and there's a massive 3-stage bonus with an escalating win potential as you progress through the stages.And watch out when the Troll King swings his hammer  the more blocks he smashes up, the higher the win! Reach your maximum win potential by upgrading all your symbols, increase the multipliers to the max, collect all 6 whirling wilds, and watch it all play out in the last 3 spins!Hall of the Mountain King is one of our biggest and most exciting releases of the year you'll definitely need to catch your breath after this thrilling gaming experience!

title: Nero's Fortune
description: Ready to travel back in time for an epic adventure? Take a trip to ancient Rome with Nero's Fortune!

title: Northern Sky
description:
In Northern Sky, you gaze upon the stunning sky to catch a glimpse of the prizes on offer, as they glisten in the bright, colourful polar light.

Set in the heart of a fictional rural landscape in northern Scandinavia, the animal-shaped symbols are made out of crystals that light up the sky and offer an avalanche of wins.

The highest paying symbols are shaped like the animals of this northern forest, such as owls, wolves and bears and the more majestic they are, the more valuable they are. The golden dear is the most majestic of them all, so this is what you want to chase!

This highly volatile 5?3 slot with nine paylines features respins on all wins, plus a Free Spins Bonus game that includes only the highest paying animal symbols!

title: Panther's Reign
description: Welcome to the jungle! Panther's Reign will take you on a once-in-a-lifetime adventure to the Amazon, a lush and vibrant paradise.Spin your way through this tropical forest and soak up the sounds of the flowing river, exotic birds and gentle breeze. Keep an eye out for colourful parrots, cheeky monkeys and shiny gemstones along the way. And the king of the jungle the elusive black panther.This colourful 50 line 4x5 slot boasts high volatility and thrilling game mechanics! The Wild Spray feature places 3-10 random wilds on the reels, and the lock-on-win Respin feature in the Free Spins bonus makes the gaming experience even more exciting.

title: Phoenix Sun
description:
Phoenix Sun is based on the ancient legends of the Phoenix bird. This mythological creature is said to live for thousands of years, eventually bursting into flames and being reborn from the ashes.

In similar fashion, our Phoenix Wild will trigger reels to open up for respins and more bet ways. The game shifts between 3 and 6 rows in height, and 243 to 7776 bet ways.

Gather 5 Phoenix Wilds during respins and watch them set the reels ablaze, only to rise again along with the sun and a round of 8 Freespins.

title: Pied Piper
description:
The legendary Pied Piper is back! But instead of chasing the mice away, everyone's invited to this joyous celebration where players can win BIG!

Set in the city of Hamelin, this man in colourful clothing has brought his pipe along to give you a really exciting gaming experience.

The central aim in this game is triggering the walking feature, where all the mice follow the Pied Piper as the game respins.

And just when you think the game is over, the Piper might return for more respins! Triggering the Free Spins will create an enhanced bonus experience as well, because as night falls over the city of Hamelin, there's even more mice to catch!

This game is jam-packed with exciting gameplay and awesome features, all to the tunes of joyful music and beautiful graphics that will rival any animation studio!

title: Pirate's Charm
description:
In Pirate's Charm, you join the brave buccaneers as they venture out on stormy seas in search of golden charms! These charms are packed with mystical powers that transform your wins.

The adventure begins as the sturdy ship slips anchor, but as the storm clouds gather, it's far from pain sailing towards the land of the buried treasure.

For those of you who are brave enough to embrace the wild weather, this extremely volatile game offers plenty of charms with respins and free spins galore!

title: Polar Paws
description: We're releasing our first Christmas game just in time for the holiday season!With a beautiful winter wonderland inhabited by cute polar bears and a generous elf who loves to throw sweets around, Polar Paws will get you into the Christmas spirit before Santa Clause has even left the North Pole.This fun-filled character game combines the happy holiday theme with modern game mechanics, like an exciting Free Spins Bonus and Wilds galore: there's Regular Wilds, Multiplier Wilds, and a Polar Bears Turn Wild feature.So if you're not already wild about Christmas, you will be now!

title: Prime Zone
description: If you're a fan of classic casino games, you're gonna love this one! We've made this slot for the true casino fans, to appeal to their gambler souls and give them something truly special.Picture a Las Vegas casino at night, with silhouettes of palm trees against the purple sky. In walks the legendary Rat Pack, Frank Sinatra, Dean Martin, and Sammy Davis Jr. Ok, maybe not, but it certainly feels like they could!This stunning 3-5 reel slot with 10 betlines combines a classic look with exciting features, like Multiplier Wilds that can multiply a win by up to 5x, and a Free Spins Bonus that lets you to pick your own volatility with the pre-bonus picker! And on top of that, we've also added a mystery (I'm Feeling Lucky) free spin mode to the mix.Mark your calendars and get ready to get in the zone!

title: Rapunzel's Tower
description:
The classic fairy tale has been given a makeover thanks to HTML5 technology, including the princess’s long locks of blonde hair, which look better than ever.

This 3×5 20-line slot provides massive wins with the stacked Rapunzel wilds, while the “Bonus Wilds stick until you win” feature means players are given a greater opportunity of wins, as The Bonus Wild symbols are locked in place and the game re-spins until a winning combination is triggered.

And make sure you hit the Free Spins bonus and make the Prince save Rapunzel from the Tower.

The reengineered slot offers stunning graphics and immersive sound across desktop, mobile, and tablet. But be quick to try out the game, as the princess is waiting for you

description:
Razortooth is a pre-historic game starring some of the coolest animals from the last ice age.

The game is the first 243 ways game produced by us, and has two major features with fantastic payout.
In the base game you can get a random triggered sequence where the Razortooth tiger leaps across the screen to leave multiple wilds behind. In the Free Spins bonus at least one reel is wild each spin.

title: Reno 7's
description: Who doesn’t have a road trip in the US on their bucket list? Imagine you’ve invited your best friends along for the trip of a lifetime. As you’re cruising down the highway together, wind in your faces and the landscape of Nevada rolling out around you, there’s nothing but blue skies and free time ahead.

title: Sakura Fortune
description:
In Sakura Fortune, you step into an enchanted world of cherry blossoms and golden dragons to join the heroine on her journey.

This extremely volatile 4x5, 40-line slot follows a beautiful Japanese princess as she battles evil emperors on her way to untold riches!

The game boasts exciting features like Sakura Fortune Respins, Free Spins, and a Mystery Nudge.

With it's action-packed, feature-rich gameplay, stunning graphics and lucrative wins, it's no wonder this game is one of our biggest hits!

title: Second Strike
description:
Second Strike is our first volatile 10 line game. Our inspiration has been the classic fruit machines with their simple but elegant game mechanics.

 Second Strike is a far cry from the old classic games though, as we have added an exciting twist, the Second Strike feature!
Any symbol win initiates the Second Strike feature. Players hitting a matching symbol on the outer wheel, will be rewarded with 6-10 additional symbols for a second massive win!

title: Sevens high
description:
Classic slot style symbols combined with contemporary club music, and staggering visual presentation makes it feel fresh and familiar at the same time.

The Progressive Wild feature has been well proven in Big Bad Wolf. In Sevens High we take the feature to another level with stacked symbols, and a Free Spin bonus where any symbols
turned wild stay that way until the bonus round is over.

title: Sevens High Ultra
description:
Tough day? Come have a good time and unwind with Seven’s High Ultra. Grab a drink and a bite to eat while you put your feet up and spin the reels.

Just like the original game, classic meets contemporary for a fresh and familiar experience. Timeless slot symbols like cherries and other fruits are matched by modern club music and exciting features – now with extra heat!

The Progressive Wild feature has been a proven success in both the original Seven’s High and Big Bad Wolf, but we’re taking it to a whole new level in Seven’s High Ultra. title: Sinbad
description:
Superb graphics and animations will be the first impression of Sinbad, but the glory of the game lies within the gameplay.

The randomly stacked symbols ensures interesting wins in main game, but really comes to play in the wild frequent free spins features. There are three different free spin bonuses to choose between, each representing one of Sinbad's adventures.

title: Skulls UP!
description: Dream of escaping someplace warm? Skulls UP! is just what you need. Set sail for riches and join the pirates, parrots and playful monkeys on this tropical island!This fun and quirky 5-reel slot will keep you entertained for hours. Hunt for hidden treasures amongst the palm trees and feel the heat from the high volatility and flaming hot features, like Flaming Free Spins, Flaming Respins, and Flaming Skull Wilds!And to turn up the heat even more, the reels can grow (up to 6 symbols in height!). Every Wild symbol you get during a Flaming Respin will open up a new position above the reelsincreasing the number of bet ways from 243 all the way up to 1,944! Arr matey, time to sail ship and discover what treasures await!

description:
Spinions is a fun-filled 25 lines game with cute and lively characters who enjoy a great summer party.

The Spinions love good times, and great company, and the game's respin feature gives them plenty of reasons to celebrate. Two Spinion Wilds trigger a respin with the Wilds stickying on the reels, and additional Spinions keep it respinning.

In the Free Spins the Spinions continue their party at the night club where all wilds are sticky and remain on the reels for the rest of the bonus.

You don't want to miss this beach party!

Your favourite orange dudes and dudettes are back and they sure know how to have a good time. Expect an all-you-can-eat buffet, delicious drinks, and dancing on the tables (there might even be karaoke if you stay long enough).

And it wouldn’t be a Quickspin bash without the brilliant features, which include Sticky Wild Respins and Sticky Wilds in the Free Spins Bonus, so grab your ugliest Christmas sweater and get ready for some seriously festive gameplay!

description:
Plunge into the wicked Wild West and join a couple of bad-ass bandits as they attempt to rob a runaway train!

Sticky Bandits is a thrill-a-minute rollercoaster of a ride, featuring desperadoes, dynamite, and a killer western soundtrack.

With high volatility, Massive Wild symbols, Bonus symbols, and a Free Spins Bonus, this slot is guaranteed to give you an exciting gaming experience!

One of our most popular and highest performing slots to date, Sticky Bandits has been so popular that we decided to release a sequel in 2019 Sticky Bandits: Wild Return!

title: Sticky Bandits 3: Most Wanted
description: Dynamite, guns, cacti, and whisky the wicked Wild West is back! The first two Sticky Bandit slots are two extremely popular Quickspin games, so who are we to deny you a third one?This time around, the bad-ass bandits are five fierce women and they've only got one thing on their mind: to get inside that locked safe and run away with bags full of cash. Will you be able to get your hands on some of it? Sticky Bandits 3 Most Wanted is a 3x5 slot loaded with exciting Wilds and Free Spins, plus the Sticky feature that everyone loves. And you don't even have to wait around for the Free Spins bonus  pay 60x bet and get instant entry with the Bonus Buy feature!

description: The old bandits are back in town, meaner and leaner. And they say all good things come in three, so we've added a new bad-ass bandit to the gang. This trio of desperadoes is ready to cause some serious havoc in a dingy saloon that's packed with whiskey, cigars, guns, and skulls just as you'd expect in the wicked Wild West!This gaming experience is every bit as thrilling as the first Sticky Bandits! The three bandits show up as both normal and massive symbols on the reels (up to 3x3!), and there's an extremely exciting shootout in the Free Spins Bonus where all the bandits can turn into Sticky Wilds!

Based on the series of classic novels from 1920, this slot pays homage to the world's most famous animal whisper.In this animal adventure, you get to hang out with the famous Dr. Dolittle and all his pets  a dog, a horse, and a parrot! This slot expands our portfolio of character games, which already includes popular games like Big Bad Wolf and Goldilocks.

description:
Jump into the fast-paced action of the Wild Chase, where you and your fellow team of thieves are planning one last heist!

Set in a glamorous resort town on the Riviera, the kind of place where the top 1% hang out, this game boasts stunning scenery, super slick graphics and a really exciting gameplay!

This slot is not only full of jewelry and expensive watches, it's also full of awesome features. Any win is rewarded with respins, and they continue as long as new wins are added! On top of that, the multiplier Wilds will multiply any win in which they are included.

If you're a fan of heist films, you're going to love this game!

description:
Looking for something a bit different for your vacation this year? Ticket to the Stars is just the ticket (pun intended)! It will take you on an exciting space adventure, filled with relaxation, romance, and wealth.

So, pack your bags and take a seat onboard this space craft – we’ll help you travel the solar system in style! Enjoy the gorgeous vintage design, inspired by vintage Work Projects Administration (WPA) posters, as well as beautiful audio compositions that are some of the best this side of Jupiter.

With tons of exciting features and a 243 way evaluation over 3×5 reels, we’ll make sure this extremely volatile game takes you on a trip you’ll never forget! They say space travel is the future, so be the first to try

Tiger’s Glory is the most epic gladiator battle in the history of slot gaming! So, get your armor on, step into the colosseum of ancient Rome, and get ready to face some seriously fierce tigers!

Our most action-packed showdown yet pits tigers against gladiators in an epic fight worthy of history books. In this extremely volatile 4×6 reel slot with 40 paylines, the action is non-stop and it’s guaranteed to keep you on your toes every step of the way!

Make sure you keep an eye out for the Enraged Tiger – this Free Spins bonus game is triggered when three or more Bonus Scatter symbols lock into place. Free spins are available whenever the tiger wins a battle, and you can get as much as 20 free spins if you’re lucky.

description:
Get whisked away to a colourful and prosperous world filled with hopping vampires. You heard right! Our July release is inspired by Chinese folklore, where undead creatures, known as the Jiangshi, appear with outstretched arms and stiff posture, preying on humans to absorb their life force.

We've placed a more comedic tone on this traditionally dark theme and packed it with plenty of suspense and anticipation. Included is a base game mystery feature, randomly creating 3-9 additional Talisman Wilds, and it doesn't stop there. The game gets even darker in Free Spins. After landing one or more Vampire Wilds, the Jiangshi will hop around, sinking their teeth into any Medium human symbol that appears next to them, creating more wilds! Appearing on a 5x5 layout, Vampire Sempai boasts invigorating colour combinations, rich graphics, and eye-catching effects that will leave the player thirsty for more!

title: Volcano Riches
description:
Volcano Riches takes you inside an active volcano where Pele, the goddess of volcanoes and fire (and creator of the Hawaiian Islands), might reward you generously with BIG wins!

This highly volatile 5x4 slot with 40 paylines is a fiery little number that makes you wish for a hot streak, and it's got tons of exciting features too!

If a Wild symbol lands on the third reel, it will explode and generate two to five additional Wild symbols in adjacent positions. These volcanoes also explode, leaving you to bask in the warm glow of your winnings  if you're lucky!

Time to feel the heat!

Welcome to the smoky back tent of an independent circus, where a talented magician owns the stage. But is she really alone up there? Or does she have a twin…?

Catch this travelling circus while you can, because once this sneaky lady has moved on with her entourage there’s no trace to be seen. Not even a dent in the field. Makes you wonder if it was all a dream…

title: Wild Tome of the Woods
description: Whittlewood Forest is a former medieval hunting ground in Northamptonshire, England, where a reclusive wizard named Tom lives. But his friends call him Middy (short for Midas) due to his life-long obsession of trying to turn things into gold. So far, he's failed.Instead, after years of having gold-related spells written into it, his Wild Tome has started to turn random things around it into gold! This causes all kinds of problems, so the wizard and his friends: the half frog/half newt Crikey, the fox Sylvester the 3rd (nicknamed Sly for obvious reasons), and the posh owl from Oxford named Eleanor, are trying to put a stop to it. But before they do, why not take advantage of the situation and grab some gold for yourself?This fun-filled 4x6 slot with 26 bet lines includes exciting features, like the Wild Tome feature that will turn other symbols into Wilds or new Wild Tomes, creating truly magical amounts of Wilds.
